      • checkMenuBar

        protected void checkMenuBar​(String menuName,
                            String expected)
                     throws Exception
        Helper method for testing a complete menu bar. Executes the script with the given builder name and compares the results with the expected text.
        Parameters:
        builderName - the builder name
        menuName - the name of the menu bar
        expected - the expected results
        Throws:
        Exception - if an error occurs
